data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully renovated home located on the desirable Emmett Bench. Spacious floor plan, kitchen features all new cabinets & counter tops, new tile backsplash, SS appliances, farm sink & custom breakfast bar. New luxury vinyl plank flooring, wood accent wall, new interior paint, lighting & ceiling fans. Abundance of windows bring in natural light. All updated electrical, newer roof, nice corner lot, RV parking, garage/shop w/power (22x20). Enjoy the summer evening on the large patio!
